snippet.title: METAL GEAR SOLID V: THE DEFINITIVE EXPERIENCE - Launch Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
METAL GEAR SOLID V: THE DEFINITIVE EXPERIENCE is the ultimate collection of the METAL GEAR SOLID V story which includes the critically acclaimed METAL GEAR SOLID V: THE PHANTOM PAIN, its prologue METAL GEAR SOLID V: GROUND ZEROES, the tactical multiplayer game as well as all their DLC content.

| METAL GEAR SURVIVE
| https://www.konami.com/mg/mgsv/

| Twitter: twitter.com/metalgear_en
| Facebook: facebook.com/mgs

Rated Mature: Blood and Gore, Intense Violence, Sexual Violence, Strong Language
